introduction.im: a Software Engineer from in Tunisia.

Index.aboutmeDesc: Hi there! I'm Mustapha Taibi, a 22-year-old computer science graduate passionate about web development and exploring new technologies. I have experience working with modern tools like Next.js, React, Node.js, Express, and MongoDB, and I'm currently learning how to integrate AI into web applications to create innovative and impactful products. I enjoy building full-stack applications and am always eager to expand my knowledge and tackle new challenges.

projectDescription.Fluent Tales: AI-powered German learning assistant. It features a comprehension section with customizable generated texts and exercises, a vocabulary section with theme generated nouns, verbs and useful phrases, a grammar practice section and a writing assistant that provides feedback based on your proficiency level.
projectDescription.Tuni-Auctions: an Auction platform built around exploring the local market, identifying its issues and introducting new and innovate solutions to help revive the market and make the bidding experience much more enjoyable.
projectDescription.Dar Seranity: Rental platform that manages the full spectrum of renting functionalities like handling home listings and requests for home viewings, monthly rent payment and tracking, and tenants move out.
projectDescription.Tuni-Work: Freelance platform that takes care of job listings, freelancer browsing and applications, project acceptance, task tracking within projects, secure payments, and a reporting system for dispute resolution with employers.
